## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible nursing interventions. Some sources may not be peer-reviewed, and the information might not be applicable to all client populations. Additionally, the effectiveness of interventions can vary based on individual client needs and conditions. Further research and clinical trials are recommended to validate these interventions across diverse settings.